# Ignore AppData and similar system-level paths if they are somehow picked up
# This is a broad exclusion, ensure your project doesn't legitimately use these paths in its structure.
# Given the error, it's likely these are outside the project root but were picked up by `git add .`
AppData/
*/AppData/
$RECYCLE.BIN/
System Volume Information/
*.lnk
